juce: juce (Cross-platform C++ framework)
juce:
juce: JUCE is an open-source cross-platform C++ application framework for
juce: creating desktop and mobile applications, including VST, VST3, AU,
juce: AUv3, AAX and LV2 audio plug-ins and plug-in hosts. JUCE can be easily
juce: integrated with existing projects via CMake, or can be used as a
juce: project generation tool via the Projucer, which supports exporting
juce: projects for Xcode (macOS and iOS), Visual Studio, Android Studio,
juce: and Linux Makefiles as well as containing a source code editor.
